Dialogue: 3,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}An Enka singer?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:54.51,0:00:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why do you have to appear with her? {Oh yeah! Mitsuki is okay to appear with a geisha instead. Meroko no Baaaka}
Dialogue: 3,0:00:57.55,0:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You {\i1}are{\i0}  an idol, aren't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I think it's because...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:02.20,0:01:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...Komaki-san has been hosting a show for new idols lately. {I feel like something's untranslated here, I will beep convex to confirm}
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.67,0:01:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, I'll be a guest on her show.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:11.51,0:01:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:12.59,0:01:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}"Do you want the next generation to live by strict rules?"
Dialogue: 3,0:01:16.78,0:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Looks like new idols have to go through this gateway for success.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}"Gateway for success?"
Dialogue: 3,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's that?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:23.22,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It means something like \Nthe road to stardom.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:28.06,0:01:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You should have said so from the start.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:30.71,0:01:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}"Gateway for success...", he said.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:33.19,0:01:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Old man Takuto... gross!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:35.77,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Haha, Meroko, you didn't \Neven know what it meant. {the and was unneeded}
Dialogue: 3,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}T-That's not true!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:42.41,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Besides, I'm older than you, Takuto!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:46.37,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, if I'm an old man, that makes Meroko an old hag, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Now you've done it! {Takuto no Baka! He transformed to get some spanking :D}
