Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:52.46,Location Note,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,410)\b1\i1\fs36}{\frz0}It's {\frz-1.5}Ko{\frz1.5}ma{\frz-1.5}ki-{\frz1.5}san! {\frz1.5}Gre{\frz-1.5}et{\frz1.5} her {\frz-1}pro{\frz1.5}per{\frz-1.5}ly!{Ooshige is talking in sign language}
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}G-Good day! {Oh no}
Dialogue: 3,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, wasn't that Komaki just now?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? That was Komaki-san?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm a failure.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why didn't you come with me?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You didn't know that was Komaki-san?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.94,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She wasn't wearing a kimono, so...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Enka singers wear jeans, too.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, did you greet her properly?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh... sort of...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm kind of worried.
