Dialogue: 3,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This time, say "Good Morning!" \Nwhen you greet her.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Here we go.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.99,0:04:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse me, this is Ooshige.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Once more, seriously this time. {Edit block}
Dialogue: 3,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This is {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}, \Nand I'm her manager Ooshige.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Good morning!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm looking forward to working with you today.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How do you do? I'm Komaki.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm also looking forward to today.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's still new, so I think she could have some problems...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, how wonderful!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}W-Wait, Mitsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wow, the kimono is so pretty.
