Dialogue: 3,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I really messed up...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And Ooshige-san doesn't \Nlook too happy either...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:42.24,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Aside from that, that Komaki's a mean old hag.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.24,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Should you be saying that?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shut it.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:50.58,0:05:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man, that Komaki's a mean old hag, right?{}
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:55.67,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And that bald manager is \Nsuch a stick-in-the-mud.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Tadokoro, is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He sure is one.{}
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's such an ass kisser.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:03.88,0:06:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Weren't you doing that to Komaki as well?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, you have no choice in order to advance your career in showbiz.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's no helping that.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Rehearsal is starting, we should get going.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:18.90,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What was that about?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's so disgusting.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Should you be saying that?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.24,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She should have put it out properly.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:26.82,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You! {It's not what it looks like, honest}
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you doing with that cigarette?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're still a teenager!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:31.32,0:06:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really... all the new talents these days...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, you're mistaken.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:36.62,0:06:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The girl who just left \Ndidn't put it out properly.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why I...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:40.29,0:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}How dare you talk back...!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Man, kids these days...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}In the old days, you wouldn't even think about doing that.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's not how it was...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She really is a mean old hag!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This girl would never smoke!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, she's really pissing me off!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, Meroko!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh... wait, you two!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Rehearsal is starting soon.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Do your best so Komaki-san \Nwon't get mad at you. {Too late}
Dialogue: 3,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Test! Test!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A! A! A!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mic check!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mic check!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Whoa!{}
Dialogue: 3,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Check, one, two!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Check, one, two!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's so many staff members here.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They're working hard \Nto broadcast your song.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.99,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san, we're on standby, so please go on.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}See, now, good luck.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:45.95,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}R-Right!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay, let's try it.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, we'll start in...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Five seconds...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:59.41,0:07:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Four.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.37,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Three.
