Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:09.80,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:14.01,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,0)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Cut!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What is she doing?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:21.16,0:08:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The camera appeared so suddenly... \NI was surprised.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We're doing the same thing this time, so please don't be startled by it, okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:28.19,0:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Alright, let's try again!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Five seconds...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.91,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Four.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:46.21,Myself Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,36)}{\k33}{\be3\fad(200,200)}Dou{\k87}shi{\k40}te {\k64}dou{\k37}shi{\k46}te {\k38}su{\k78}ki {\k40}na{\k38}n{\k36}da{\k27}ro{\k54}u
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:52.76,Myself Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,36)}{\k40}{\be3\fad(200,1512)}Ko{\k59}nna {\k90}ni {\k38}na{\k26}mi{\k54}da {\k15}a{\k25}fu{\k35}re{\k23}te{\k243}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:46.21,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Why... just why have I fallen in love with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:52.76,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\be3\fad(200,1512)}Yet, still... I can't stop my tears from falling...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}After the intro, start the lasers...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}Ready and go!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Whoa, whoa! {Deadly lazors}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Cut!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:07.27,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Does she think something will happen if the lasers touch her?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's clean up and start with Komaki-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:15.34,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Alright then, let's get moving!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:18.28,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Excuse me, you can take a short break now, so if you could tell {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.24,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Standby, and get ready!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:23.79,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Alright.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll try to calm her down.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, please do.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Take a break!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:51.15,0:09:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What exactly is your reason to fly out here, leaving her all alone?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:57.99,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There's the one. {edited}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:58.91,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}There! That guy!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}From that magazine she was reading last night... one of the band members!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'll be on TV with her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}He's so cool!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hello?!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Weren't you looking for Komaki?!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Geez, you're so annoying.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}A little distraction won't hurt.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Could it be...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe you're jealous?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why should I be jealous?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.65,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Maybe because this is the date\N that I've longed for?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, it's too bad that \NI had to leave her by herself.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.90,0:10:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh, you're such a sinner, Meroko...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}And to think you're a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Komaki Fuyuko is hard to deal with.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I was so tense the whole time, Takeda-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I never even knew you could think that way.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Please stop making fun of me.{edited}
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.05,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey Meroko!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Those guys... weren't they reporters from "Monthly SuperStar"?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The ones who just passed by?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't be so weak, Nou-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That Komaki-san must have a good side, too.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.45,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But there are so many rumors spreading.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That she's hard to deal with... and that she picks on the newcomers...{}
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I heard those too. I'd hate to say\N that those were true.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She probably does those things \Nbecause she cares.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:23.16,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To show that she's there to help them...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.95,0:11:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She was forced to be an idol, or so I heard.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:31.66,0:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She didn't like her debut song, \Nbut she had to sing it.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She was depressed and \Nbegan to smoke and drink.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.27,0:11:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}As a result, she ruined her voice.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:43.03,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Her attitude that we see now...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...is probably the result of that.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:49.69,0:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even so, did she really have a good voice?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Somehow, she could light up people's hearts.{Timing}
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Nowadays, you can't find \Nsingers like that anymore.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:06.03,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why she got angry that time.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She might be a good person after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.50,Sign (Komaki Dressing),,0,0,0,Sign For TS,{\fs24\fscx89\fscy89\pos(329.515,392)}Komaki Fuyuko-sama's \NDressing Room
Dialogue: 3,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's see...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}They took a break and \Nsaid that Sensei's turn is next.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:18.55,0:12:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, I said that we can't do that, but the director insisted.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:23.84,0:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}R-Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:26.91,0:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Honestly, what was that novice thinking?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She was rude to you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}This time, she messed up the schedule.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:34.75,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's a really rude person, isn't she, Sensei?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei!{}
Dialogue: 3,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what we heard.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So that's why.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:48.12,0:12:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I must have sounded so rude\N to Komaki-san earlier.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, I have to apologize to her properly.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Komaki-san's entering.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm going.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm really sorry, Komaki-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Alright, alright, stop playing around.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You should go outside.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:13.59,0:13:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But, I...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's this about?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's time for Sensei's recording.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:24.49,0:13:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If you do anything bad, it may throw off Sensei's performance.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why did that guy throw Mitsuki out?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm sure it's because Komaki said so.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just like I thought, she is a mean old hag!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She's really a troublesome novice, isn't she?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's take out {\i1}Full Moon's{\i0}  performance. {Screw you, hage}
Dialogue: 3,0:13:47.47,0:13:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Just put Sensei's new single instead.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}S-Sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait a sec! What is he saying?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, we have to tell her.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:55.76,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? They're not letting me sing?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Seems like it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I knew it! She's definitely evil!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's so... cruel.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why are you canceling \N{\i1}Full Moon's{\i0}  performance?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Can't help it.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.99,0:14:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She was so troublesome to Sensei.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:17.81,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's why we're changing our schedule.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei doesn't have free time like you do.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Even so, that is too cruel.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Mitsuki?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Komaki-san?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:37.18,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Komaki-san, they said that they won't let me sing... is that true?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? But Tadokoro-san said that...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.34,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Is she plotting something?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I know I've been in your way \Nmany times, Komaki-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But not letting me sing is just too much!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's my first time on TV.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to sing... quickly.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Quickly what?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}To quickly become a big star that everyone idolizes about?{Edited}
Dialogue: 3,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, what is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If that's not true, why else do you want to become a singer?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I promised...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I made a promise...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...to someone very dear to me. {Taisetsu=Important/Special, but this flows better imo}
Dialogue: 3,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Someone very dear to you?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:17.84,0:15:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't know where he is now.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:20.97,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But we made a promise...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that we'd both work hard \Nto achieve our dreams.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, please, let me sing.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You're too naive. {naïve}
Dialogue: 3,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's just a dream.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:32.84,0:15:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Once you get into it, \Nthe promise will be forgotten.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You will sing and sing because it is your job.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}No, I won't!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:41.12,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:45.21,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Then Komaki-san is singing\N because it's her job?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:51.09,0:15:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Of course.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That's what makes me a pro.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't think that way.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I don't think that way!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:00.14,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I want to sing with that \Nprecious feeling inside me.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}If I can't do that, then I'm fine \Nwith not being a pro.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.80,0:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}All I want is to touch people's \Nhearts with my songs!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, {\i1}Full Moon{\i0}-san, please.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh? But they said I wouldn't sing...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's alright.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The idea was from this rotten bald guy.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can sing.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:40.53,0:16:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:44.02,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We'll take it from the top!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Five seconds...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:48.81,0:16:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Four.
