Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:28.56,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}I couldn't sing at all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:33.03,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}That place you had to leave for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:40.66,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}It happened to be the place where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:47.00,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}On that day I could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:52.00,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}{\c&H7DC0FF&\3c&H002449&\2c&HD2ECFF&}The desolation lying in your eyes
