Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:11.06,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Why do I love you so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:17.03,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}Your voice is calling out with such sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:23.37,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,200)}I never knew what was supporting me, back then, and even now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:31.00,Myself TL,,0,0,0,,{\be3\fad(200,840}Until we became so far apart...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(200,00)}Promise me.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.20,0:17:13.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(00,200)}The next time we meet, we will be closer to reaching our dreams.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:14.82,0:17:15.48,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}Well, she has the potential to be an idol.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}Yeah, I think so too.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}Wait, please.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}I want to sing Enka!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.01,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}Wait, please!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}I don't think that way!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:50.52,0:17:54.62,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}I want to sing with that precious feeling inside me.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:54.62,0:17:58.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}If I can't do that, then I'm fine with not being a pro.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:58.51,0:18:03.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}{\fad(0,100)}All I want is to touch people's hearts with my songs!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}She's wonderful.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\pos(320,430)}She's just like a young Komaki Fuyuko.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:32.63,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei?{So deserving. How about one on his right too?}
Dialogue: 3,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Why did you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Don't even bother to come \Nto work from tomorrow.{}
Dialogue: 3,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Sensei...!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Ah, Komaki-san!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Eh, Takeda-san too?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:52.65,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(60,115)}You've been involved with new idols lately.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(60,115)}How are they?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}{\fad(60,115)}The latest idol, in particular...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Let's see.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Today, the girl didn't greet me properly.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.85,0:19:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She looked at my kimono and said that it was like in a Shichigosan.{}
Dialogue: 3,0:19:04.52,0:19:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She even had enough energy \Nto mess up my schedule.{}
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I couldn't even imagine that one person could mess up that badly.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}That sounds so troublesome.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She was different from all the newcomers I've come across.{}
Dialogue: 3,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}She even dared to voice her opinions to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:23.80,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Oh...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm ashamed to admit it, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:27.41,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}...that girl reminded me of what's important when you become a singer.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Once again, I want to go back \Nto my original intentions.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Well, Komaki-san, she seems to have left a deep impression on you.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:41.99,0:19:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}It's possible she made me realize my situation.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:48.62,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}So, until we meet again, \Ndo your best, Miss Newcomer.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1\pos(320,435)}I will!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:34.81,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Takuto, there's trouble!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}The paparazzi are onto her!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.81,0:21:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}At this rate, her secret will...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:41.27,0:21:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}We can't let her secret get out!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:45.70,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait for me, Mitsuki!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.82,0:21:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I'm coming to help you!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:47.78,0:21:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Wait!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}You can't do it alone!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:51.10,0:21:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Shut up!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I will...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}I will always protect her!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.45,0:21:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\be1}Dangerous Lens
